  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>An unusual alternative to the traditional jetpack, this flight device is sculpted from the remains of sentient rock. Magmatic gases provide the hardpack's thrust, while an anti-gravity field supports the weight of the stone, ensuring ergonomic safety for the user.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>与传统喷气背包截然不同的替代选择，这种飞行设备完全是拥有智慧的石头残骸雕刻而成。磁性气体为硬质背包提供推进力，反重力场则支撑着沉重的石头，这种符合人体工程学的设计能够很好地保障使用者的安全。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>這個飛行裝置與傳統的噴射背包大為不同，是以有知覺的石頭為材料雕刻而成。硬包以岩漿氣體為推進器動力，內含反重力場支撐石頭的重量，確保裝備符合使用者人體工學。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
